      {
        "text": "###Farming \n\nFarmers use **AI and computers** to study pictures from satellites or drones to see:\n\n\n- If plants are sick and how to help them\n- Exactly when and where to deliver water",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/c592d31507d0a8521a0940f803ed8ea5-FarmingPanel.gif",
        "key": "hardware-components-e56bb056-0af5-475f-b8e1-7b49f9c79f82",
        "layout": "text-bottom-right",
        "typing": false,
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      },
      {
        "text": "####Health Data Expert\n- AI helps find sickness in X-rays, like broken bones or infections.\n- This helps doctors spot problems early.\n- Their work makes care smarter and faster! ",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/a11427e2a0bc62c57dc9b2d4d3b61081-HealthCarePanel.gif",
        "key": "hardware-components-ed2b07b1-278f-49d5-ba3b-02994f4bccd8",
        "layout": "text-bottom-right",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      },
      {
        "text": "###Fitness App Coder\n\n- They use code and AI to track moves and workouts.\n- Apps give smart tips to stay healthy.\n- Tech that helps you stay active! ",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/352e0d66b3ffd4dc616caf593f76a21b-FitnessAppPanel.gif",
        "key": "test-elem-career-journeys-explore-panels-efeae7e1-8db4-4614-b904-07eedf4ef555",
        "layout": "text-bottom-right",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      }
    ],
